54
00:07:01.129 --> 00:07:03.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Der kann was, der rote Flieger.

55
00:07:07.635 --> 00:07:09.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
