94
00:11:35.945 --> 00:11:38.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Der will wohl Eindruck schinden.

95
00:11:53.754 --> 00:11:56.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
